Justin Carmack https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Justin_Carmack 0 Justin Matthew Carmack (March 12, 1981 – July 20, 2000) was an American child actor, known for his appearance in the television series Full House. He died on July 20, 2000 in a traffic accident in California. He was buried on the Santa Ana Cemetery.
